 studying the topic (the eight categories), one attains the four preparations\/applications (this is the purpose), and attainment of the four preparations\/applications is necessary for the attainment of Buddhahood (the final purpose).<\/p>","title":"An Overview of the Purpose Section and So Forth"}]}
